title: HOUR 1 – Sputtering Seahawks

description:
Colin reacts to the Seahawks loss to the Rams last night, is joined by former Super Bowl champion and NFL analyst Johnathan Vilma, and why OBJ’s lack of production last night isn’t a big deal.
